03/09/2009
ATHENS, Greece -- Authorities announced on Wednesday (September 2nd) they have found eight anti-tank rockets in a forest area near Thessaloniki. The discovery was made by finance ministry fraud inspectors who were acting on a tip. The National Intelligence Service and the police anti-terror department have been informed. According to authorities, the rockets were made in the United States and were "carefully packaged". (ANA-MPA, AP - 02/09/09)
